This is the GridAgent Server, version 2.1.

It implements the (new) GridAgent Server Protocol, versions 1 and 2.

Options are specified in agentserver/settings.py

Database access is via the Django ORM, through models specified in our GridPlatform project (i.e. the GridPortal 2.0 models).


To run in development:
* make and enter a Python virtualenv
* run "setup.py develop" for gridplatform
* run "setup.py develop" for gridagentserver-protocol
* run "setup.py develop" here ...
* start.sh
